had Samji]]<br>Sparsh Khetarpal<br>Tasha Bhambra<br>Madhur Sharma\n|-\n! Story\n| colspan=\"3\" | Sajid Nadiadwala\n|-\n! Cinematography\n| [[Binod Pradhan]]\n| colspan=\"2\" | Santhana Krishnan Ravichandran\n|-\n! Editor\n| Manan Sagar\n| colspan=\"2\" | Rameshwar S. Bhagat\n|-\n! Composer(s)\n| [[Meet Bros]]<br>[[Amaal Mallik]]<br>[[Ankit Tiwari]]<br>[[Manj Musik]]<br>Pranaay Rijia\n| [[Mithoon]]<br>[[Arko Pravo Mukherjee|Arko]]<br>[[Sandeep Shirodkar]]<br>Gourov-Roshin<br>Pranaay Rijia\n| [[Vishal\u2013Shekhar]]<br>[[Tanishk Bagchi]]<br>[[Sachet\u2013Parampara]]<br> [[Rochak Kohli]]<br>Pranaay Rijia\n|-\n! Background Scored By\n| colspan=\"3\" | [[Julius Packiam]]\n|}\n\n==Release and revenue==\n{{unreferenced section|date=March 2020}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:75%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:centr;\"| Film\n! style=\"text-align:centr;\"| Release date\n! style=\"text-align:centr;\"| Budget\n! style=\"text-align:centr;\"| Worldwide Box Office\n|-\n| ''[[Baaghi (2016 film)|Baaghi]]'' ||  29 April 2016 || {{INR|37 crore}} || {{INR|125.92 crore}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movie/baaghi-3/box-office/|title=Baaghi Box Office Collection till Now - Bollywood Hungama|website=Bollywood Hungama}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Baaghi 2]]'' || 30 March 2018 || {{INR|59 crore}} || {{INR|254.33 crore}}\n|-\n| ''[[Baaghi 3]]'' || 6 March 2020 || {{INR|85 crore}} || {{INR|137.57 crore}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movie/baaghi-3-2/box-office/|title=Baaghi 3 Box Office Collection - Bollywood Hungama|website=Bollywood Hungama}}</ref>\n|-\n! Total ||  || {{INR|181 crore}} || {{INR|515.82 crore}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}6.  [https://onlylyrics.in/baaghi-3-full-movie-download/ Baaghi 3 Full Movie Online Download Information]\n", "text_old": "{{Primary sources|date=March 2020}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2020}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Baaghi (film series)\n| image          = \n| caption        = Collage of Movie Po